As part of the Digital Avatar RAG system, we are building AI responses for device-related queries. To ensure complete, structured data ingestion, we request access to the following device-related information in a structured API format or export:

ðŸ”¹ Standard Device Metadata (for mobile/tablets):

Device ID / Unique SKU

Brand, Model Name

Release Date

Screen (Size, Type, Refresh Rate)

Camera Specs (All lenses separately)

Storage Options

OS & Chipset (if available)

Available Colors

Virtual Device Availability

Device Category (IoT, Mobile, Hotspot, etc.)

Associated Plans / Promotions

ðŸ”¹ Category-specific Metadata (if applicable):

Coverage Devices: Area coverage (sqft), Devices supported, Handoff details

IoT Devices: Use cases, sensors, compatibility, supported plans

Accessories: Type, compatible devices

ðŸ”¹ Metadata Needed for AI Contextualization:

Short description or marketing copy

Links to device detail pages

Thumbnail image URL

Tags or keywords (business, enterprise, mobile internet, etc.)

Weâ€™re happy to work with your team to align the API response format. Let us know if any of this data is unavailable via API so we can plan alternative ingestion methods.


